sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Player
    participant Modal as DifficultyModal
    participant GS as GameSettings (static)
    participant MDM as MapDataManager (-> MapSession)
    participant Loader as MapLoader (-200)
    participant Applier as GameSettingsApplier (-150)
    participant GM as GameManager (-100)
    participant TM as TrainingManager
    participant G as Ghost / Pacman

    Note over U,Modal: ChoixTypeJeu scene
    U->>Modal: pick map + difficulty pips + ghost toggles + autopilot
    Modal->>GS: set speed/duration levels, SetGhostEnabled, AutopilotEnabled
    U->>Modal: click "Jouer" (StartGame)
    Modal->>GS: PendingAutopilotLaunch = AutopilotEnabled (one-shot)
    alt Map 2 selected
        Modal->>MDM: currentMap = ImportMap(secondMap.json)
    else Map 1 (default)
        Modal->>MDM: currentMap = null
    end
    Modal->>Modal: SceneManager.LoadScene("Pacman")

    Note over Loader,GM: Pacman scene loads (DefaultExecutionOrder)
    Loader->>MDM: read currentMap
    alt custom map selected
        Loader->>Loader: rebuild tilemaps, spawn pellets, NodeGenerator
    else default scene map
        Loader->>Loader: do nothing
    end

    Applier->>GS: read speeds / durations / exit delays
    Applier->>G: movement.speed, PowerPellet.duration, GhostHome.SetDuration

    GM->>GM: Awake: singleton + FilterEnabledGhosts(GameSettings)
    GM->>GM: build ScoreManager / LivesManager / UIManager
    G->>G: Ghost.Awake: resolve movement/home/scatter/frightened/chase
    GM->>GM: Start: SetScore(0), SetLives(3), NewRound()
    GM->>G: ResetState (ghosts + Pac-Man)
    GM->>GM: ApplyRoundSpeeds (per-round curve)

    opt PendingAutopilotLaunch or ML training/inference scene
        TM->>GS: read PendingAutopilotLaunch (then clear it)
        TM->>G: AgentActivator.SetActive(true) -> Pacman.aiControlled = true
        TM->>GM: trainingMode = true
    end
